---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="Terms of Service | TikaTiles"
			description="Terms of service for the TikaTiles website and game prototype."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="legal-page prose">
			<p class="legal-kicker">Last updated: June 25, 2026</p>
			<h1>Terms of Service</h1>
			<p>
				These Terms of Service govern your use of tikatiles.com, including the TikaTiles
				game prototype and product information shown on this website. By using this website,
				you agree to these terms.
			</p>

			<h2>Prototype Status</h2>
			<p>
				TikaTiles is an early-stage product concept and prototype. Product designs, features,
				availability, pricing, safety certifications, app features, game mechanics, and
				hardware specifications may change before any commercial release.
			</p>

			<h2>Website and Game Prototype</h2>
			<p>
				The games on this website are provided for exploration, feedback, and demonstration.
				They do not represent the full functionality, safety behavior, performance, or final
				appearance of any future physical product.
			</p>

			<h2>Permitted Use</h2>
			<p>
				You may use the website for personal, non-commercial evaluation. You may not interfere
				with the website, attempt unauthorized access, copy the site for competing commercial
				use, or use the site in a way that violates applicable law.
			</p>

			<h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
			<p>
				TikaTiles names, designs, copy, game concepts, graphics, code, and other materials on
				this website are owned by TikaTiles or used with permission unless otherwise stated.
				No rights are granted except the limited right to access and use the website.
			</p>

			<h2>Feedback</h2>
			<p>
				If you share suggestions, ideas, bug reports, game concepts, or other feedback, you
				allow TikaTiles to use that feedback without restriction or compensation. Please do
				not send confidential information through this website.
			</p>

			<h2>No Warranties</h2>
			<p>
				The website and prototype games are provided as is and as available. TikaTiles makes
				no warranties that the site will be uninterrupted, error-free, secure, or suitable for
				any particular purpose.
			</p>

			<h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
			<p>
				To the fullest extent permitted by law, TikaTiles will not be liable for indirect,
				incidental, consequential, special, punitive, or exemplary damages arising from use
				of this website or prototype.
			</p>

			<h2>Changes</h2>
			<p>
				These terms may be updated as the product and website evolve. Continued use of the
				site after an update means you accept the updated terms.
			</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>
				Questions about these terms can be sent to
				<a href="mailto:info@tikatiles.com">info@tikatiles.com</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.legal-page {
		padding-top: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
	}

	.legal-kicker {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-indent: 0;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.legal-page h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
		line-height: 0.95;
	}

	.legal-page h2 {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3vw, 2rem);
	}

	.legal-page p {
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		text-indent: 0;
	}
</style>
